The following activities are prohibited without prior written permission from the copyright holder:

* Selling, sublicensing, relicensing, or otherwise commercializing the Software itself.
* Redistributing the Software, whether modified or unmodified, as a standalone plugin, framework, toolkit, library, or competing product.
* Publishing compiled binaries of the Software for public distribution.
* Uploading, selling, or distributing the Software, whether modified or unmodified, through marketplaces, asset stores, plugin stores, package repositories, or similar distribution channels.

Any distributed copy of the Software or derivative works must retain this copyright notice and license text.

